message: "If you use Penumbra in your research or teaching, please cite it."
title: "Penumbra: a privacy-preserving perpetual multi-agent arena"
type: software
authors:
  - family-names: "Vadale"
    given-names: ""
repository-code: "https://github.com/Vadale/penumbra-arena"
license: MIT
